data.description:
Assumable 2.75% interest rate VA-Mortgage comes with this gem; secluded towards the end of a cul-de-sac - yet close to all the shopping in Harker Heights. Plenty of natural light brighten up the entire living area and breakfast area with multiple window fronts. 
Practical and well coordinated tile flooring in all living, dining and wet-areas make maintenance a breeze. 
Relax on your gazebo-ready deck, in your nice-sized privacy fenced back yard while watching the Texas sunset. 
Schedule your showing ASAP!
